### Cloud Accounts

- Amazon Web Services 
    - Access is granted via GitHub org access and uses [AWS SSO](https://ministryofjustice.github.io/modernisation-platform/concepts/environments/single-sign-on.html#single-sign-on) and membership to GitHub teams to define account access.
- Microsoft Azure
    - [Azure Landing Zone](https://dsdmoj.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/PTTPWIK/pages/3454107649/Engineer+Onboarding#Azure-Tenant-IDs-and-Subscription-Access) access to Confluence is needed, you can drop a message in [#techops-team](https://mojdt.slack.com/archives/CSAD2TAA1) channel and someone in the team will help you.

